These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
House: farmhouse, wooden, futuristic, modern
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, grey, mauve, amber
1. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
2. the person who likes amber is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes mauve is between the person who likes grey and the wooden house##2
4. the modern house is on the far left##1
5. the futuristic house is between the wooden house and the farmhouse house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| House   | modern         | wooden   | futuristic | farmhouse       |
| Color      | amber | white | mauve   | grey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, fisherman, entrepreneur, pilot
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, water, lemonade, fanta
1. the person drinking fanta is between the entrepreneur and the person drinking water##2
2. the pilot is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
4. the architect is on the left of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Job         | fisherman | architect | entrepreneur | pilot |
| Beverage   | water    | fanta   | milk | lemonade       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, guinea-pig, rat, turtle
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, prince, bolivar, bluemaster
1. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
2. the bolivar-smoker is between the prince-smoker and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
3. the prince-smoker is on the far left##1
4. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is the bluemaster-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Pet          | turtle    | ferret | guinea-pig   | rat  |
| Cigar   | prince | bolivar   | bluemaster | dunhill |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-4::.
There 4 different types of food: onion, cauliflower, cranberry, asparagus
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, dahlia, tulip, balloon-flower
1. the person who growsdahlia is the person eating cauliflower##1
2. the person eating onion is between the person who growszinnia and the person eating asparagus##2
3. the person who growsdahlia is on the far right##1
4. the person eating onion is on the right of the person who growstulip##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Food     | asparagus   | onion    | cranberry       | cauliflower   |
| Flower   | tulip | balloon-flower | zinnia | dahlia |

