.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-5::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, iris, lily, begonia
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, june, february, august
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who growslily##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far right##1
4. the person who growsbegonia is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in june##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2     |     3     |       4       |
| Flower   | balloon-flower        | lily | begonia  | iris |
| Birthday      | february | june  | august | april    |

