.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, collecting, singing, filmmaking
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, horse, rat, pony
1. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the owner of the rat##1
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is collecting##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Hobby   | collecting     | singing           | rock-climbing | filmmaking  |
| Pet         | rabbit | pony | horse   | rat |

