.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, whist, chess, monopoly
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, mystery, romance, comedy
1. the person playing whist is the person watching animation movies##1
2. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
5. the person playing backgammon is between the person watching animation movies and the person playing chess##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Game   | monopoly   | whist | backgammon | chess      |
| Movie-Genre     | romance | animation    | mystery  | comedy |

