.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
4 different games are played: snooker, poker, scrabble, go
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, trance, indie, ambient
1. the person playing scrabble is between the fan folk and the person playing snooker##2
2. the fan ambient is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
3. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
4. the fan folk is on the left of the fan ambient##1
5. the person playing snooker is on the left of the fan indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Game         | poker | scrabble | snooker | go |
| Music-Genre   | folk         | ambient       | trance    | indie         |

