.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, camping, skydiving, traveling
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, helicopter, jet-ski, airplane
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person driving the helicopter is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person driving the airplane##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Hobby    | traveling   | skydiving      | camping   | writing  |
| Transport   | airplane | helicopter | jet-ski | roller |

