.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, ice-hockey, badminton, parkour
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, writing, puzzles, video-games
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person who's sport is lacrosse##2
3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Sport          | lacrosse     | ice-hockey | parkour   | badminton        |
| Hobby   | singing | puzzles   | writing | video-games |

