.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, ice-hockey, soccer, cricket
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, coral, light-blue, grey
1. the person who likes light-blue is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
2. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
3. the person who likes blood-red is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
4. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who likes coral##1
5. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
6. the person who likes coral is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who's sport is cricket##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | soccer | cricket | biathlon |
| Color   | light-blue          | coral     | grey  | blood-red     |

