.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-13::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, september, august, october
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, black, coral, lilac
1. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person who likes lilac and the person who's birthday is in november##2
3. the person who likes black is on the far right##1
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who likes coral##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Birthday           | november | october | september | august     |
| Color   | turquise   | coral    | lilac   | black |

