There 4 different types of food: pineapple, avocado, zucchini, cherry
1. the owner of the lizard is the person eating zucchini##1
2. the person eating pineapple is between the person eating cherry and the person eating avocado##2
3. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
4. the person eating cherry is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
5. the person eating zucchini is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| Pet           | hamster | horse | goat | lizard |
| Food   | avocado   | pineapple | cherry         | zucchini |

