.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-15::.
City: new-york, marseilles, london, colone
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, february, june, july
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
2. the person traveling to colone is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person traveling to new-york##2
3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |      4       |
| City         | new-york      | colone | marseilles  | london |
| Birthday   | february | june  | july | september    |

