.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-17::.
4 different games are played: whist, mah-jongg, canasta, chess
There 4 different types of food: garlic, pumpkin, carrot, watermelon
1. the person playing whist is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
2. the person playing chess is the person eating carrot##1
3. the person eating pumpkin is between the person eating garlic and the person playing mah-jongg##2
4. the person eating watermelon is the person eating watermelon##1
5. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person eating carrot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Game   | chess | mah-jongg | whist | canasta |
| Food           | carrot  | watermelon  | pumpkin | garlic      |

