House: craftsman, farmhouse, colonial, tower
1. the farmhouse house is on the left of the tower house##1
2. the craftsman house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is the craftsman house##1
4. the tower house is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in august##2
5. the person who's birthday is in august is the colonial house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Birthday   | february   | march   | july | august |
| House         | craftsman | farmhouse | tower     | colonial    |

