.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, bike, skateboard, helicopter
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, april, september, august
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the taxi is between the person who's birthday is in november and the person driving the helicopter##2
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
4. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Transport   | skateboard    | helicopter     | taxi | bike |
| Birthday     | april | august | september       | november     |

 